quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  44,40,"Pellet, ko √ëalnde Darngal, woni ko Allah saatini senndindirgol hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen, …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe, tuma …ìe moo…ìindiraa."
  44,41,"√ëalnde nde gi…óo woo nafoytaa gi…óo mun ; …ìe wonaali kadi da…óoo…ìe lepte Allah …óen, tawde Laamu ngun nden √ëalnde, ko Allah woodani, wanaa go…ó…óo e nodditoraynoo…ìe ngu."
  44,42,"Si wanaa ne…ó…óo mo Allah yurmaa woo, on …óon nafitoroy golle makko mo∆¥∆¥e …óen. Pellet, Allah ko Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake, Hinnotoo…óo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  44,43,"Pellet, leggal Zaqquumi ngal Allah fu…óini ngal ka asli Yiite,"
  44,44,"Ko ngal woni √±aamdu …óuu…óu…ìe bakkaatu …ìen, woni heefero o na nyaama e …ìesnooje makki co…ì…óe …óe."
  44,45,"Nde …ìesnaande na nanndi e nebban …ìale nde taayinaa, hara hino fata e deedi ma…ì…ìe …óin, hakkee ko wuli."
  44,46,"Wano ndiyam wul…óam jaw nguli fatirta."
  44,47,"Ayninaay…ìe Yiite ngen wi'anee: nanngee mo poo…óiron doole, haa ka hakkunde Jahiimi."
  44,48,"Refti yuppon ka hoore makko, ndiyam fasnaa…óam …óam, hara o seertataa e lepte …óen."
  44,49,"O wi'anee ontuma: awa mee…óu non lepte muusu…óe …óen ! An sikkunoo…óo ko a foolu…óo mo dartetaake, teddu…óo hakkunde yim…ìe mun."
  44,50,"Awa ko …óee lepte woni ko sikkitino…óon si laatotono √ëalnde Darngal sikke iwii e mon caggal On fellitii hannde."
  44,51,"Pellet, hulir…ìe Joomi mun …ìen …óoftagol Mo ha…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko, …ìen wonii e weerde hoolniinde e kala bone."
  44,52,"E nder gese e …ìulli ilay…ói."
  44,53,"Hi…ìe …ìoornoo ka Aljanna ton, comci …óaatu…ói e tekku…ói, hara hi…ìe fewtondiri, …ìe runtandirtaa."
  44,54,"Ko wano Men teddiniri …ìe non …óin jantaa…ói, Men resiniri …ìe kadi ka Aljanna, rew…ìe yaaju…ìe gite, tii…óu…ìe …ìaleeri gite."
  44,55,"Hi…ìe golloo…ìe ton …ìen, fii addangol …ìe kala muuyantee…ói …ói …ìe faaletee, hara ko …ìe hoolii…ìe e anngal ta∆¥ondirgol …ói maa lorra majji."
  44,56,"Ko …ìe duumotoo…ìe ton, …ìe mee…óataa ton maayde woo, si wanaa maayde aranere nden aduna, Joomi ma…ì…ìe da…ónda …ìe lepte Yiite ngen."
  44,57,"∆äum ko dokkal e mo∆¥∆¥ere immorde ka Joomi maa. Haray ko jantaa koo, e naadeede …ìen Aljanna, da…ónda …ìe Yiite, ko …óum woni maloore mawnde nden, nde sugu mun alaa."
  44,58,"Ko Men newinirani ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinirgol nde e …óemngal maa, aarabu ngal, an Nulaa…óo, ko no …ìe waajitora."
  44,59,"Habbito faabo maa ngon e halkeede …ìe nden. Kam…ìe ko …ìe habbitii…ìe maayde maa."